{"tid":493149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"動漫迷遇襲案　5被告表證成立下周結案陳詞","createTime":"2017-12-08T08:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T11:32:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1dcb81b0a362e79572ca0ab65485aa09352facf1","tid":493149,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/photo/bkn-20171208133807232-1208_00822_001_01p.jpg?20171208163643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171208%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171208133807232-1208_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20171208163643&h=919874d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男動漫迷疑得罪女動漫迷，並於網上羞辱拒絕過他的女子，事後遭人設局毆打兼拍片向所有女動漫角色扮演者(女Coser)道歉一案，今日(8日)於區院續審。代表次被告邵頌然的律師早前反對其口供等呈堂，指次被告當時受警員恐嚇及利誘，非自願地作出，法官今裁定不接納次被告的口頭招認及書面供詞。5名被告被裁定表證成立，他們不自辯，案件押後下周待辯方進行結案陳詞。 <br />\n<br />\n控方庭上分別讀出第三至第五被告的口供。被事主羅浩峰指是「未來戰士」第三被告溫穎賢，在口供中指當日因喜歡玩cosplay，故到九展看展覽，他又指自己喜愛扮演遊戲街頭霸王的「軍佬」一角。他表示案發前已認識首被告「玲瓏」陳顯華，對方相約他當日到九展教訓一個周圍騷擾coser的男子。溫承認曾掌摑網名「司徒奈奈」的事主左邊面，腳踢其左膝及打其肚一下。溫指以為事主道歉後便完事，怎料同行女子卻再打事主，他「唔想睇落去」而轉身離去，他並沒有搶事主的東西。溫指事後已感後悔，並與有關人士斷絕來往。 <br />\n<br />\n而被指是「肥仔」的第四被告曾柏豪在口供中，否認有打過事主，亦看不到有人搶事主的東西，但見到其他人毆打事主。 <br />\n<br />\n被指是「皮褸」的第五被告趙文俊在供詞中承認有打事主，亦拿走事主80港元買了一個插頭。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/mobile/bkn-20171208133807232-1208_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171208%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171208133807232-1208_00822_001.html&d=sx1eECieIWN3UKPoJM0ceNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=e546776a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/mobile/bkn-20171208133807232-1208_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f4c5d8567beb22835679354a2afd2b3b53757d52","tid":493149,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:27:00.000Z","msg":"星期一連登仔一齊去幫明眼人打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/180203_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F180203_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ba800665&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6eae34aebb93e0173da5858099ec44e250849f8","tid":493149,"uid":47521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:30:16.000Z","msg":"係女Coser呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1d2160f134411d8d19cf1e3814079d89cbdf26","tid":493149,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"下星期一灣仔區域法院，連登仔一齊去幫明眼人打氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/192956_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F192956_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6799bbc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/180203_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F180203_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ba800665&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"b5afb6e6efdab5f230045bdb4831992ae7fb27ff","tid":493149,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}